trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of attributes that can be accessed by name or index.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av attributter som har tilgang til navn eller indeks.

trans-unit.source: `XmlAttributeCollection` extends the <xref:System.Xml.XmlNamedNodeMap> class by adding strongly typed helper methods.
trans-unit.target: `XmlAttributeCollection`utvider den <xref:System.Xml.XmlNamedNodeMap>klassen ved å legge til sterkt skrevet helper-metoder.</xref:System.Xml.XmlNamedNodeMap>

trans-unit.source: You can use this class to add, remove, or modify attributes in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne klassen for å legge til, fjerne eller endre attributtene i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: `XmlAttributeCollection` is returned by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement.Attributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: `XmlAttributeCollection`returneres av den <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement.Attributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Xml.XmlElement.Attributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
